snippet.title: Pixel Cup Soccer   Ultimate Edition
snippet.description:
Pixel Cup Soccer - Ultimate Edition is a casual retro style soccer game, a great evolution from the previous edition. It's dynamic, arcade, with a fast paced gameplay, with just the fun part of soccer! The game has pixel art graphics with the retro style of the games from the 90’s, evoking nostalgia!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1620540/Pixel_Cup_Soccer__Ultimate_Edition/
